{
  "page": "10,000 Ships",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This article is about the planned television series. For the legend, see <a href=\"/index.php/Ten_thousand_ships\" title=\"Ten thousand ships\">Ten thousand ships</a>. For the book, see <a href=\"/index.php/Ten_Thousand_Ships\" title=\"Ten Thousand Ships\">Ten Thousand Ships</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary navbox-title\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-style: italic; background-color:&#91;&#91;:Template:Infobox television/colour&#93;&#93;;\">10,000 Ships</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre</th><td class=\"category\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">Fantasy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Developed by</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eboni_Booth\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Eboni Booth\">Eboni Booth</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eboni_Booth\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Eboni Booth\">Eboni Booth</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country of origin</th><td>\nUnited States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language(s)</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Production <span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">company(s)</span></th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:&#91;&#91;:Template:Infobox television/colour&#93;&#93;;\">Chronology</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Related shows</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>10,000 Ships</b></i> or <i><b>Ten Thousand Ships</b></i> is the working title of a planned American <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">fantasy</a> television series, taking place a thousand years before the events of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> to explore the story of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynish</a> warrior-queen <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Production\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Production</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Conception_and_development\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conception and development</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Casting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Casting</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10,000_Ships&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>10,000 Ships</i> takes place a millennium before the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>, focusing on Nymeria and her <a href=\"/index.php/Ten_thousand_ships\" title=\"Ten thousand ships\">exodus</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, leading the survivors of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> after they were defeated in a <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">massive war</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrians</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Production\">Production</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10,000_Ships&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Production\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conception_and_development\">Conception and development</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10,000_Ships&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Conception and development\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>10,000</i> ships was first announced in March 2021,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> with Amanda Segel enlisted as writer later that year in May.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> While Segel's involvement was announced on May 25, 2021, the project has not yet been greenlit to full production, nor did Segel receive a formal pilot order: the announcement was that Segel had been hired to write a formal pitch script.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Writer <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Helgeland\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Brian Helgeland\">Brian Helgeland</a> revealed he had work on the project in 2017, prior to Amanda Segel. He was unsuccessful to pass the development phase of the project, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As of June 2024, the project is still in development at HBO. <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> revealed that playwright and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulitzer_Prize_for_Drama\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Pulitzer Prize for Drama\">Pulitzer</a> winner <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eboni_Booth\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Eboni Booth\">Eboni Booth</a> is now writing a new pilot for the project.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Casting\">Casting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10,000_Ships&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Casting\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>TBA as <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10,000_Ships&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Hollywood Reporter: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/all-the-game-of-thrones-spinoffs-in-the-works-at-hbo-4153435/\">All the \"Game of Thrones\" Spinoffs in the Works at HBO</a> (March 19, 2021)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Deadline: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://deadline.com/2021/05/game-of-thrones-amanda-segel-write-10000-ships-spinoff-1234763526/\">Amanda Segel To Write \"10,000 Ships\" Spinoff</a> (May 25, 2021)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/159070-10000-ships-in-development-at-hbo/&amp;tab=comments#comment-8685465\">Ran's comment</a> (May 25, 2021)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Variety: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://variety.com/2024/tv/news/game-of-thrones-spinoff-ten-thousand-ships-story-queen-nymeria-1235978637/\">10,000 Ships Revealed as Moses-Inspired Epic About Queen Nymeria's Exodus</a> (April 23, 2024)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Not A Blog: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2024/06/11/awards-season-2/\">Awards Season</a> (June 11, 2024)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody>